Last week, I had insomnia, and at midnight, I dizzily got out of bed and walked to my office, opened my computer, and typed the following:
 &ldquo;There is a voice in my head telling me to write, and like a blind man I feel my way through each word, each letter, it feels right.:&rdquo;
 In the original version, in my sleepy stupor, I misspelled two words: blind and word.
